Package com.enhancell.remote

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Connection
    Connection interface provides access to a single client.
    Connection.Listener
    Listener interface for getting notified of changes in device configuration.
    Device
    Device class provides access to the network parameters measured by a UE.
    Device.Listener
    Listener interface for observing changes in the UE's parameter values and state changes.
    Manager.Listener
    Listener interface that notifies of found connections.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Device.DeviceStates
    DeviceStates class contains the state flags for describing the UE's state.
    Device.Errors
    Errors class contains defines for device errors.
    Device.Events
    Events class contains the constants for event IDs.
    Device.LockStatus
    This class lists the currently active bands and bands that are supported by the current device.
    Device.ScriptStates
    ScriptStates class contains the constants for observing the progress of the scripts.
    Device.StateMessages
    StateMessages class contains constants for messages that indicate state change
    Device.Systems
    Systems class contains the constants for system IDs.
    Device.Value
    This class wraps the parameter values reported by the UE.
    GpsLocation
    Wrapper class for Android's Location class that provides some additional information, namely HDOP and number of satellites.
    Manager
    Manager class that provides access to the client connections using Bluetooth.
